direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **/rfe.create**

  Problem statement
  `--headless`
  `--priority`
  `--labels`
  `--rfe-id`
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 0: Parse Arguments ---

parse: |md
  **Parse Arguments**

  Extract flags:
  `--headless`, `--priority`
  `--labels`, `--rfe-id`
  Remaining = idea text
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 1: Load Rubric ---

rubric: |md
  **Load Rubric**

  Check `artifacts/rfe-rubric.md`
  If missing:
  `bootstrap-assess-rfe.sh`
  `/export-rubric`
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 2: Clarifying Questions ---

clarify: |md
  **Clarify** _(interactive)_

  Ask PM 2-5 questions:
  Customers, justification,
  user problem, scope, success
  Adapt to rubric criteria
| {style.fill: "#dbeafe"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

headless-skip: |md
  **skip**
  _(--headless)_
| {style.fill: "#fef9c3"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 1; style.stroke-dash: 3}

# --- Step 3: Generate RFEs ---

generate: |md
  **Generate RFEs**

  Apply `rfe-template.md`
  Size: S / M / L / XL
  WHAT + WHY only
  One RFE per need
  Acceptance criteria
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Step 4: Write Artifacts ---

assign: |md
  **Assign IDs**

  `next_rfe_id.py <count>`
  or use `--rfe-id`
  Allocate RFE-NNN
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

write: |md
  **Write Files**

  `artifacts/rfe-tasks/RFE-NNN.md`
  `frontmatter.py set`
  `frontmatter.py rebuild-index`
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Output ---

output: |md
  **Done**

  Edit artifacts
  `/rfe.review` next
  or re-run `/rfe.create`
| {style.fill: "#d1fae5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Edges ---

entry -> parse
parse -> rubric
rubric -> clarify
rubric -> headless-skip: "--headless" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
headless-skip -> generate {style.stroke-dash: 3}
clarify -> generate: "answers"
generate -> assign
assign -> write
write -> output
